SmartColumnScroller
ver. 0.21 (17 January 2011)

Copyright 2011 Dusan Hlavaty [ dhlavaty@gmail.com ]

In multicolumn page layout, automatically scrolls smaller column
so user never sees white space underneath. 

Licensed under the MIT:
http://www.opensource.org/licenses/mit-license.php

Example:
http://dhlavaty.github.com/jQuery-SmartColumnScroller/

Usage:

  jQuery(window).load(function () { 
    jQuery('#myDiv').smartColumnScroller();
  });

Recommendation:
  start plugin processing in 'window.load' event and not in 'document.ready'